Manufacturer: Lenovo
Model Name: Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Yoga
Model Number: 

Notes:
This device uses an AES pen, reportedly with a supercapacitor instead of 
a battery.

    0003:056A:503E.0001.hid.bin   Wacom Touch
    0003:056A:503E.0002.hid.bin   Wacom Pen

There are apparently multiple versions of the X1 Yoga available, some which
use the 056a:503e sensor and others which use the 056a:503f sensor.

